Package: redistverse
Title: Easily Install and Load Redistricting Software
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c( person(given = "Christopher T.", family = "Kenny", role =
        c("aut", "cre"), email = "ctkenny@proton.me", comment = c(ORCID
        = "0000-0002-9386-6860")), person(given = "Cory", family =
